## 8. Required API surface

Base path:

```text
/v1/sessions/{session_id}/replit
```

Plan routes:

```text
POST /plans
GET /plans
POST /plans/{plan_id}/revise
POST /plans/{plan_id}/approve
```

Task routes:

```text
GET /tasks
POST /tasks
GET /tasks/{task_id}
POST /tasks/{task_id}/queue
POST /tasks/{task_id}/start
POST /tasks/{task_id}/ready
POST /tasks/{task_id}/apply
POST /tasks/{task_id}/dismiss
POST /tasks/{task_id}/cancel
GET /tasks/{task_id}/logs
GET /tasks/{task_id}/diff
GET /tasks/{task_id}/test-results
```

Checkpoint routes:

```text
GET /checkpoints
POST /checkpoints/{checkpoint_id}/rollback
```

Error rules:

- `404` for missing plan/task/checkpoint
- `409` for invalid state transition
- `422` for invalid request payload
- `500` only for unexpected server failure

